{"tid":656332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用LED照射貓頭鷹，受不鳥人類滋擾搬家","createTime":"2018-05-07T07:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T07:20:02.000Z","uid":20430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4eb15ea4756092b833d4ceaaa0de0f0a026d99e5","tid":656332,"uid":20430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T07:20:02.000Z","msg":"【慈雲山貓頭鷹BB】疑受電筒光滋擾 貓頭鷹搬家了！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖︰網民攝得貓頭鷹BB相片，惟有網民亦拍得有人把電筒長時間照向貓頭鷹寄居的樹上。（Facebook圖片）<br />\n【慈雲山】慈雲山「萌爆」貓頭鷹BB，連日來吸引大批市民及「龍友」到場「朝聖」；不過，部份「龍友」為拍得「靚相」竟用電筒，長時間射向領角鴞貓頭鷹一家寄居的鳳鳯木樹上，貓頭鷹一家疑受電筒光滋擾，現已移居附近另一棵樹上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖︰大批市民及「龍友」有持相機長鏡，希望拍得貓頸鷹「靚相」。（慈雲山資訊交流facebook圖片）<br />\n慈雲山道一公園近日發現有領角鴞貓頭鷹出現，吸引大批市民和「龍友」到場拍攝，康文署雖已築起圍欄禁止市民接近鳥巢，並於鐵欄加上寫有警告字句的告示，惟有市民聲稱因「唔開燈影唔到」，將電筒綑綁在鐵欄上，照向貓頭鷹寄居的樹上，希望拍得貓頭鷹照片。<br />\n<br />\n貓頭鷹BB學飛 群落人群中<br />\n<br />\n有網民則拍得貓頭鷹BB學飛期間，「降落」拍照人群之中。其他網民回應指︰「每日咁多人探佢，己習慣了，唔怕人！」，亦有人擔心貓頭鷹安危︰「慘啦當人係親戚！無左警覺性。岀去揾食實死响(在)人手上。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖︰網民Johnny Yuen攝得照片，指貓頭鷹BB學飛期間，「降落」於拍照人群之中。（Facebook圖片）<br />\n根據《野生動物保護條例》野生雀鳥，包括貓頭鷹，均受保護，任何人干擾野生雀鳥、鳥巢及鳥蛋均屬違法，一經定罪，最高可被判罰款10萬元及監禁一年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/151418_7d2954dab0d286667aebec5db5904e40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F151418_7d2954dab0d286667aebec5db5904e40.png&h=afd96cc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/151419_017dcd03a1a12f5a986a746679fa23c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F151419_017dcd03a1a12f5a986a746679fa23c4.png&h=f692ff73&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/151421_c1ec6079ac0f801485e060d295c023d3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F151421_c1ec6079ac0f801485e060d295c023d3.png&h=8190fcf3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/151426_582556f85798c8734e6de4ccbd456704.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F151426_582556f85798c8734e6de4ccbd456704.png&h=2ad1736b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/151430_311f55ed995e1a80003dfd7e8a5fb12f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F151430_311f55ed995e1a80003dfd7e8a5fb12f.png&h=303e9e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/151433_d32a41f21a40fa674f3ee90a9289f467.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F151433_d32a41f21a40fa674f3ee90a9289f467.png&h=adbde3d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/151436_b80b1814ae92a4bdbe7bfc163788eed5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F151436_b80b1814ae92a4bdbe7bfc163788eed5.png&h=caea344e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/151438_bbdad4c834daa0ad67a277a5c6abefd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F151438_bbdad4c834daa0ad67a277a5c6abefd5.png&h=67410e43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n照返你睇下你難唔難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}